These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, orange
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, photography
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy
1. the person watching epic movies is not to the right of the person eating orange##8
2. the person eating orange is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
3. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | 7up      |
| Food          | orange | pineapple    |
| Hobby         | photography   | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | fantasy      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, engineer
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, jet-ski
1. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the project-manager##5
3. the engineer is not to the right of the project-manager##8
4. the person driving the subway is not the person who's hobby is reading##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | fanta        | water    |
| Hobby       | skydiving         | reading |
| Job         | engineer | project-manager   |
| Transport   | subway               | jet-ski  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, spy
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, country
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, egyptian
2 different pets are kept: fish, goat
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the egyptian is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation       | spy |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | country    |
| Nationality   | canadian | egyptian |
| Pet           | fish        | goat   |

 #################################

 
